OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNo need for specific       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fspiking law, government    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fsays                       
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The government has said it will not    
OL,6, create a specific offence for spiking, 
OL,7, arguing a new law is unnecessary.      
OL,9,FMinisters said they were looking into  
OL,10,Fthe issue last year.                   
OL,12,FBut on Wednesday, Home Office Minister 
OL,13,FSarah Dines said there were already    
OL,14,Fseveral offences which covered spiking 
OL,15,Fincidents and the government had not   
OL,16,Ffound "any gap in the law".            
OL,18,FSupporters of the idea argue it could  
OL,19,Fhelp increase reporting of incidents   
OL,20,Fand improve police data.               
